OL,14,     Ffarmer's field, Jacko takes part
OL,15,     Fin a major heroin bust, and rookie
OL,16,     Fpolice dog Elsa chases a runaway
OL,17,     Fburglar through the streets of
OL,18,     FMiddlesbrough.
